  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业IoT系统的架构图。整体分为三个区域：客户端、边缘网关和服务器端。客户端有四个主要组件，主要是TelemetryStream、ActuatorController这些工业设备。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cliente",
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "C4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个子图结构。我注意到C1和C3都是TelemetryStream，这是有意设计的吗？还是笔误？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是有意的。C1是上游采集端，C3是下游反馈端，虽然类型相同但在流程中位置不同。C2是ActuatorController负责执行控制，C4是PLC_Logic做逻辑运算。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "C3",
        "C4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那边缘层Vite只放一个MQTT_Broker作为P1，充当协议转换和边缘汇聚的角色，这样理解对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Vite",
        "P1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，P1是边缘MQTT Broker，负责把客户端数据汇聚后转发到云端服务器。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "服务器端Servidor我打算放五个节点：S1和S3、S5都是MQTT_Broker做集群，S2是ActuatorController，S4是PLC_Logic。这样形成高可用链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Servidor",
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "S1、S3、S5都是Broker？那数据流怎么走？S2和S4在中间起什么作用？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我的设想是：C1→C2→P1→S1，然后S1→S2→S3→S5是一条主干，同时S2还要分叉到S4再到S5，形成冗余路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C2",
        "P1",
        "S1",
        "S2",
        "S3",
        "S4",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "这个拓扑可以。S2作为控制器要同时处理实时流和逻辑校验，S4的PLC_Logic做异常检测，两条路径最后在S5汇聚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S2",
        "S4",
        "S5"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "主干链路已画好。现在处理反馈回路：S5要连回客户端的C3，这里需要标注一下传输内容。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S5",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "S5到C3的返回数据要包含JSON格式的控制台输出、错误日志、符号表和AST抽象语法树，这是调试诊断用的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S5",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加带标注的连接线。最后C3还要连到C4完成闭环，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C3",
        "C4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，C3收到诊断数据后交给C4的PLC_Logic做本地策略调整，形成完整控制回路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C3",
        "C4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我检查一下：C1和C3都是TelemetryStream类型，但C1在流程起点发数据，C3在终点收数据，这样会不会让人混淆？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C1",
        "C3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
